{"tid":1652322,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【路障攻略】","createTime":"2019-10-13T15:45:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-09T17:34:52.000Z","uid":106368,"like":42,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"5f8a4cdfc79b9db65df55f38c2fd3f1ceaca3d28","tid":1652322,"uid":106368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T15:45:47.000Z","msg":"今日見到某區手足好執著起幾層三角鐵馬 有啲野想講<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  錯誤示例  <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div><br />\n<br />\n1. 用塑帶紥三角鐵馬<br />\n望落好實淨又好似好疊馬 其實狗用𠝹刀𠝹一下就解開 連腰都唔駛彎就可以輕易搬走 <br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">阻敵時間：5秒</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mikaFMK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmikaFMK.jpg&h=e7eb57ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 用塑帶紥長方形鐵馬<br />\n狗一樣用𠝹刀𠝹一下就解開<br />\n材料同時間比三角鐵馬需要更多<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">阻敵時間：3秒</span><br />\n<br />\n3. 水馬/鐵馬就咁擺路中間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n狗可以直接移走<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">阻敵時間：最盡2秒</span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">正確示例</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1bRhkN2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1bRhkN2.jpg&h=cf20bef3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n於竪立水馬 / 三角鐵馬前方不少於15米擺放雜物陣（鐵馬、垃圾、磚、空樽）<br />\n咁樣可以有效阻擋狗向前衝的速度 減低狗行動力 爭取撤退/轉場時間<br />\n另外可加上適當油、水、皀水 隨機應變 睇到時就手有咩材料<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">阻敵時間：1分鐘或以上 睇有咩雜物</span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">升級玩法 （如果時間/人手許可）</span></div><br />\n<br />\n扭鬆路邊紅色消防喉<br />\n當狗向前跑嗰陣使用水魔法 如果可以配合油/番皀效果更佳<br />\n可以阻擋畜龍 亦都可以滅龍蛋 <br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">大家謹記，設立路障之目的：<br />\n1. 防護<br />\n2. 卻敵<br />\n3. 阻延（令大家有空間及時間快閃）</span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">千期千期唔好打陣地</span></span></div><br />\n<br />\n另外個人意見<br />\n除非附近有可見之火警及即時對民居有危險，與及有重大事故，否則要請消防及救護車另行繞路而行 請現場手足自決<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />祝各位 武運亨昌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div>"},{"pid":"adbcb244b8a8a3129db6e0d87dc0cbf9b5b5f0bd","tid":1652322,"uid":285261,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T15:49:00.000Z","msg":"遊行個個帶件垃圾掉係馬路<br />\n做路障<br />\n斷狗揸車追截之路"},{"pid":"4ec70479a4b8f8514f20ade88c58ac78950877e5","tid":1652322,"uid":106368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T15:51:47.000Z","msg":"自推10次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X7PCkSO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX7PCkSO.jpg&h=da52fd93&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/10/13/235140_826387cb5dcc5b320c5cd01f50662256.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F10%2F13%2F235140_826387cb5dcc5b320c5cd01f50662256.jpeg&h=f7a6926c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ca78a0fb50cf04295bb0c9ab4c34caf4b0a29d6a","tid":1652322,"uid":125453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T15:52:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69b0ff4a92480f8fb313ce8ba2bbf5e4425e2602","tid":1652322,"uid":106368,"like":0,"d